<ul><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/HikoninSentaiAkibaranger" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/HikoninSentaiAkibaranger">Hikonin Sentai Akibaranger</a></em> features two. Kozkoz Mita dresses as a different <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/SuperSentai" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/SuperSentai">Super Sentai</a> heroine every episode, and Yumeria Moegi is most often seen in a catgirl outfit, but has other costumes as well.
</li></ul></div>
